{"type": "article", "id": 44181, "title": "明明是卖手帕，却能让人像欣赏鲜花一样驻足观赏，怎么做的？", "description": "手帕的意义已经变化，美感和质地成了它的第一要务。", "date": "2017-08-16T23:11:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3974, "name": "互动"}, {"id": 10882, "name": "布料"}, {"id": 41959, "name": "布料设计"}, {"id": 43271, "name": "Yuri Himuro"}, {"id": 43272, "name": "swimmie"}], "category": 17, "author": 699147, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170817003029Oa5XWzRFEnp2uUwM.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>日本布料设计师 Yuri Himuro 为手帕品牌 swimmie 设计了新系列的手帕。以“鲜花”为主题，她一共设计了四款，配色和花样都不同，不过图案的布局都是一致的，沿着方巾的一条对角线，依次生长出绿叶和鲜花；如果从绿叶的那一角将手帕提起，它就会变成一把花束。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003100QkhmqxMfn0VAguTI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003059m2JnpgoXK3rxlcdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003059TANjHPOzQ4uvkDRe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003100Ya2vhFOSHb7RKPsZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Yuri Himuro 用这些手帕，在东京的 CASE Gallery 举办了一场名为 FLOWERS 的展览。不同款式的手帕，在狭窄的盒子状展厅中依次排开，从天花板上高高低低地悬挂下来。有趣的是，如果你在路边观察一会儿，会发现被“折”成花束状的手帕，会突然从高处掉落下来，“啪”地一下展开，呈现出完整的花样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003132irmeyoX9qWHtJzDC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708170031362T0XCe8fQG4cDsBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003132yjUmLCBxOZ76H3GI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003133RxeL0P6EBgApYjWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>走进展厅内，你会发现其中的玄机。天花板上隐藏了一组传动装置，手帕通过细线与之相连。这个传动装置会定时转动，手帕的位置也会随之进行调整。悬挂在较顶端的手帕，是花束状的，只有被垂落到最底部，才会伸展成方形。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003311FDQZ5otL7CN1nPwE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003201SeHKWhjxPtwFscy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Yuri Himuro 设计过不少小而美的纺织品。不过她并不满足静态的美感，而会时常加入一些小把戏，让整件作品在好看的同时变得好玩。“鲜花”系列的花束样式，不是最有趣的。在更早之前推出的 “snip snap” 系列，互动性要强得多。</p><p>Yuri 将布料设计成多层，消费者可以自行拿出剪刀，通过裁剪表层的布料，构筑新的图案。比如在以“里山”为主题的布料上，你可以在一端将平整的绿色丝线剪断，让它们变成立体的小草或柏树枝叶；或者干脆将一大片绿色丝线完全剪光，露出蓝色的丝线，将其变成池塘、小河或瀑布。总之，你可以在这块布料上，修建出你想要的田园风光。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003359L1heN3TtiODGYgHv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708170033596DWw5gl4EFjz80r7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003400FAIOVt0LqBeanrWS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003400H6P9WYVUzA2MJZI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>“motion-textile”系列，则隐藏着双重图案，从不同的角度观察，人们可以看到不同的花样。比如“sakura”（樱花），从右侧看是樱花树夏天时的模样，枝叶郁郁葱葱，而从左边看，则是春天樱花盛开时的景象。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003524thZX48reMIaCR6m0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.979592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708170035249HYFCtOUZPidEVXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003525yKbMCPfGi2zQ78T1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">而在“umi”（海洋）中，右边是海底世界，有一些小鱼混杂在蓝色的水波图案中，而左边则是海面之上的景象，有立在沙滩上的遮阳棚，还有从水面飞过的海鸟。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003553Dab9WV4oLKPgfprO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817003553A3GHJNf7awCOghrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708170035546WDJwCHUiqVf2rzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.979592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自 <a href=\"http://www.h-m-r.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">h-m-r</a></p>"}